## âœ… PRE-DEPLOYMENT CHECKLIST

Before deploying, make sure you have:

- [ ] All files downloaded from /outputs
- [ ] Files placed in correct directories
- [ ] Node.js installed (v16+)
- [ ] Firebase CLI installed
